<!-- BELIEF SYSTEM -->
<section class="belief" id="belief">
  <div class="belief-inner">
    <div class="belief-header reveal">
      <p class="section-label">The Belief System</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Twelve Ancient Herbs.<br><em>Twelve Intentions.</em></h2>
      <p class="belief-intro">
        In Traditional Chinese Medicine, every herb carries a specific energetic frequency.
        We've matched the twelve most powerful botanicals to the twelve emotional struggles
        modern life puts us through.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="belief-grid">
      <div class="belief-card reveal">
        <span class="belief-card-num">01</span>
        <div class="belief-herb">Agarwood</div>
        <div class="belief-herb-cn">沉香 · Chen Xiang</div>
        <p class="belief-emotion">Anxiety · Overthinking</p>
        <h3 class="belief-name">A Quiet Mind</h3>
        <p class="belief-desc">Agarwood settles the heart. When the world feels like too much, its warmth brings you back to your breath - to right now. Anxiety is temporary. Your roots run deep.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="belief-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <span class="belief-card-num">02</span>
        <div class="belief-herb">Ginseng</div>
        <div class="belief-herb-cn">人参 · Ren Shen</div>
        <p class="belief-emotion">Fatigue · Burnout</p>
        <h3 class="belief-name">Vital Energy Returns</h3>
        <p class="belief-desc">Ginseng replenishes what exhaustion drains. Your body's tiredness can be healed. Your spirit's weariness can be rekindled. You are allowed to rest, and then to rise.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="belief-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <span class="belief-card-num">03</span>
        <div class="belief-herb">Rose</div>
        <div class="belief-herb-cn">玫瑰 · Mei Gui</div>
        <p class="belief-emotion">Love · Heartbreak</p>
        <h3 class="belief-name">The Open Heart</h3>
        <p class="belief-desc">Rose moves stagnant energy from the liver, the organ of grief. Love isn't losing yourself - it's remaining whole while being fully known by another person.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="belief-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <span class="belief-card-num">04</span>
        <div class="belief-herb">Cinnabar</div>
        <div class="belief-herb-cn">朱砂 · Zhu Sha</div>
        <p class="belief-emotion">Protection · Boundaries</p>
        <h3 class="belief-name">Sacred Boundary</h3>
        <p class="belief-desc">Cinnabar has guarded energy fields for millennia. You have the right to protect your own. Not everything that approaches deserves access to what's inside you.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- EMOTIONAL SOLUTIONS -->
<section class="emotions" id="emotions">
  <div class="emotions-inner">
    <div class="emotions-header reveal">
      <div>
        <p class="section-label">Emotional Solutions</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">What do you<br><em>need right now?</em></h2>
      </div>
      <p class="emotions-intro">
        Every emotional struggle has a corresponding herb.<br><br>
        This isn't superstition - it's intention made tangible.
        Each time you glance at your wrist, the bracelet is a
        quiet reminder of the commitment you made to yourself.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="emotion-grid">
      <div class="emotion-card reveal">
        <div class="emotion-icon" style="background:rgba(74,113,101,0.1);">
          <span class="emotion-icon-glyph" style="color:var(--wengyan);">息</span>
        </div>
        <p class="emotion-tag" style="color:var(--wengyan);">Sleep · Rest · Calm</p>
        <h3 class="emotion-name">Agarwood Sleep Bracelet</h3>
        <p class="emotion-sub">For the ones who lie awake. Who can't stop the mind from running. The warm wood scent soothes the nervous system and gently invites deep sleep back in.</p>
        <div class="emotion-herbs">
          <span class="herb-tag" style="color:var(--wengyan);border-color:rgba(74,113,101,0.3);">Agarwood</span>
          <span class="herb-tag" style="color:var(--wengyan);border-color:rgba(74,113,101,0.3);">Sour Jujube</span>
          <span class="herb-tag" style="color:var(--wengyan);border-color:rgba(74,113,101,0.3);">Reishi</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="emotion-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="emotion-icon" style="background:rgba(184,150,58,0.1);">
          <span class="emotion-icon-glyph" style="color:var(--yingse);">福</span>
        </div>
        <p class="emotion-tag" style="color:var(--yingse);">Abundance · Career · Flow</p>
        <h3 class="emotion-name">Golden Sandalwood Bracelet</h3>
        <p class="emotion-sub">For those feeling stuck, invisible, or financially afraid. Golden wood activates the belief that abundance is your natural state, and action is your path back to it.</p>
        <div class="emotion-herbs">
          <span class="herb-tag" style="color:var(--yingse);border-color:rgba(184,150,58,0.3);">Sandalwood</span>
          <span class="herb-tag" style="color:var(--yingse);border-color:rgba(184,150,58,0.3);">Tiger's Eye</span>
          <span class="herb-tag" style="color:var(--yingse);border-color:rgba(184,150,58,0.3);">Cinnamon</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="emotion-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="emotion-icon" style="background:rgba(196,144,128,0.1);">
          <span class="emotion-icon-glyph" style="color:var(--chizhang);">愛</span>
        </div>
        <p class="emotion-tag" style="color:var(--chizhang);">Love · Healing · Vulnerability</p>
        <h3 class="emotion-name">Rose Heart Bracelet</h3>
        <p class="emotion-sub">For anyone recovering from heartbreak or learning to trust again. Rose's gentle warmth helps the heart grieve fully, then slowly - on its own terms - open again.</p>
        <div class="emotion-herbs">
          <span class="herb-tag" style="color:var(--chizhang);border-color:rgba(196,144,128,0.3);">Rosebud</span>
          <span class="herb-tag" style="color:var(--chizhang);border-color:rgba(196,144,128,0.3);">China Rose</span>
          <span class="herb-tag" style="color:var(--chizhang);border-color:rgba(196,144,128,0.3);">Rose Quartz</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="emotion-card reveal">
        <div class="emotion-icon" style="background:rgba(123,120,69,0.1);">
          <span class="emotion-icon-glyph" style="color:var(--jiaoyi);">定</span>
        </div>
        <p class="emotion-tag" style="color:var(--jiaoyi);">Grounding · Focus · Steadiness</p>
        <h3 class="emotion-name">Moss Wood Grounding Bracelet</h3>
        <p class="emotion-sub">For the scattered mind, the restless spirit, the person who can't seem to land. Earthy green anchors you in this moment. One step. Then the next. That's enough.</p>
        <div class="emotion-herbs">
          <span class="herb-tag" style="color:var(--jiaoyi);border-color:rgba(123,120,69,0.3);">Mugwort</span>
          <span class="herb-tag" style="color:var(--jiaoyi);border-color:rgba(123,120,69,0.3);">Frankincense</span>
          <span class="herb-tag" style="color:var(--jiaoyi);border-color:rgba(123,120,69,0.3);">Obsidian</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="emotion-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="emotion-icon" style="background:rgba(74,113,101,0.1);">
          <span class="emotion-icon-glyph" style="color:var(--wengyan);">護</span>
        </div>
        <p class="emotion-tag" style="color:var(--wengyan);">Protection · Energy · Resilience</p>
        <h3 class="emotion-name">Cinnabar Ward Bracelet</h3>
        <p class="emotion-sub">For empaths and sensitives who absorb what's around them. Ancient cinnabar creates an invisible boundary - your energy belongs to you, and not every room deserves all of it.</p>
        <div class="emotion-herbs">
          <span class="herb-tag" style="color:var(--wengyan);border-color:rgba(74,113,101,0.3);">Cinnabar</span>
          <span class="herb-tag" style="color:var(--wengyan);border-color:rgba(74,113,101,0.3);">Tourmaline</span>
          <span class="herb-tag" style="color:var(--wengyan);border-color:rgba(74,113,101,0.3);">Calamus</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="emotion-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="emotion-icon" style="background:rgba(184,150,58,0.1);">
          <span class="emotion-icon-glyph" style="color:var(--yingse);">健</span>
        </div>
        <p class="emotion-tag" style="color:var(--yingse);">Vitality · Strength · Renewal</p>
        <h3 class="emotion-name">Ginseng Vitality Bracelet</h3>
        <p class="emotion-sub">For those running on empty for too long. Ginseng and astragalus call your life force back home. You were born with immense energy. This helps you remember that.</p>
        <div class="emotion-herbs">
          <span class="herb-tag" style="color:var(--yingse);border-color:rgba(184,150,58,0.3);">Ginseng</span>
          <span class="herb-tag" style="color:var(--yingse);border-color:rgba(184,150,58,0.3);">Astragalus</span>
          <span class="herb-tag" style="color:var(--yingse);border-color:rgba(184,150,58,0.3);">Amber</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

