<!-- RITUAL -->
<section class="ritual" id="ritual">
  <div class="ritual-inner">
    <p class="section-label">The Ritual</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Three steps to finding<br><em>your herb</em></h2>
    <div class="ritual-steps">
      <div class="ritual-step reveal">
        <div class="step-circle">I</div>
        <h3 class="step-name">Name Your Struggle</h3>
        <p class="step-desc">Before choosing, sit quietly and honestly name what's weighing on you. Anxiety? Exhaustion? Grief? The naming is itself the first act of healing - not judgment, just truth.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ritual-step reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="step-circle">II</div>
        <h3 class="step-name">Follow Your Instinct</h3>
        <p class="step-desc">Browse and notice what pulls you. One bracelet will hold your gaze longer. A colour will feel like relief. You don't need to intellectualize it - your body already knows.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ritual-step reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="step-circle">III</div>
        <h3 class="step-name">Set Your Intention</h3>
        <p class="step-desc">When the bracelet arrives, hold it. Speak your intention aloud or in your mind. From then on, every glance at your wrist is a quiet reminder: I am worth taking care of.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

